reviewText: 2012 Supernova was very inaccurate, for the space center they show one of the buildings at KSC; however, the route they take to the space center is through desert country with mountains.  #1 Florida does not have any mountains, #2 the road to KSC is bordered on each side by swamps not desert, and #3 Florida does not have any desert.  Megafault was much better.

Some people may not like B movies or whatever but, I love these disaster flicks and if you go into these movies with an open mind and not a critic then you should enjoy it as well.. need to find more of these!

Only got this because it's one of the films of Brittany's I haven't seen yet. It's typical Asylum grade stuff, but the fact this wonderful woman is no longer with us makes it better somehow...

Great for having friends over, ordering some pizza and chucking back some beer and having a MST3K party if you can't seriously get into it. Cinema snobs, or Academy members need not apply; this movie wasn't made for you.
